fields.name: 1990s diamond-quilted shoulder bag
fields.description:
Boasting the signature diamond quilting introduced by Gabrielle Chanel in 1955, this burgundy shoulder bag from Chanel is crafted from soft lambskin. With a single flap closure, the piece features the acclaimed interlocking CC turn-lock fastening in polished gold-tone hardware.
The bag is in great condition!
Please find me a loving home!

fields.name: 1995 Paris limited edition Double Flap shoulder bag
fields.description:
A timeless design from the Maison, the Double Flap shoulder bag from Chanel Pre-Owned is the pinnacle of sophistication. Presented in a Paris limited edition, it's expertly crafted from white diamond-quilted lambskin and finished with refined gold-tone hardware.
Never worn before!
Please find me a loving home!

fields.name: GG Marmont crossbody bag
fields.description:
The interlocking 'GG' hardware on Gucci's bag is inspired by a '70s belt buckle from the brand's archives. This quilted leather style has a suede-lined interior spacious enough to carry a compact, wallet and keys. Wear yours cross-body by the chain-trimmed shoulder strap.
I have some slight damage, but nothing that can't be fixed.
Please find me a loving home!

fields.name: GG Marmont super mini quilted leather shoulder bag
fields.description:
Gucci's archives contain some truly iconic bags, including the 'Soho Disco', 'Dionysus' and 'GG Marmont'. This super mini version of the latter has been made in Italy from soft quilted leather and detailed with a burnished plaque. It's perfect for occasions when all you need to carry is a lipstick and cardholder.
Please find me a loving home!
